WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:01.266
Kill him!

2
00:00:02.700 --> 00:00:04.533
Who are you trying to kill?

3
00:00:04.533 --> 00:00:05.333
Zhao Ju

4
00:00:05.766 --> 00:00:06.766
Why are you here?

5
00:00:06.766 --> 00:00:07.866
Arrest me

6
00:00:09.300 --> 00:00:10.100
Hello

7
00:00:10.666 --> 00:00:12.600
Hey, it's not Zhao Ju.

8
00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:14.266
It's Teacher Tang

9
00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:16.833
You're done.

10
00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:18.833
Take away

11
00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:22.600
Go up without regret

12
00:00:24.766 --> 00:00:26.700
Let's go back first

13
00:00:29.933 --> 00:00:31.133
What's going on here?

14
00:00:31.133 --> 00:00:33.633
My friend found evidence of their crime

15
00:00:34.166 --> 00:00:35.966
Now you don't have to worry anymore

16
00:00:35.966 --> 00:00:38.266
Okay, you did me a favor.

17
00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:42.166
But I can't forgive you for my dad

18
00:00:42.166 --> 00:00:43.833
It doesn't matter if you forgive me or not

19
00:00:43.966 --> 00:00:45.166
Here's the thing.

20
00:00:45.366 --> 00:00:47.033
You have to stay with me.

21
00:00:47.866 --> 00:00:48.833
Why is that?

22
00:00:49.266 --> 00:00:52.466
Because I think your second uncle is just a pawn

23
00:00:52.466 --> 00:00:54.000
There is a black hand behind this

24
00:00:54.100 --> 00:00:55.500
You need my protection

25
00:00:57.133 --> 00:00:59.033
I could have you by my side

26
00:00:59.366 --> 00:01:00.866
But you better behave yourself

27
00:01:15.500 --> 00:01:16.433
Follow

